Prosecution took two months and more than 100 pieces of evidence to accuse Aaron Hernandez of killing Odin Lloyd in June 2013 .
Hernandez's lawyers called five witnesses to testify on Monday before resting at 3pm .
The defense's first witness was Dr. David Greenblatt, a professor at Tufts University School of Medicine who testified that PCP can cause people to be suddenly violent, even days after smoking .